title: Anjana Singh geared up to rock Doha on Eid
text:
Just like last two year, this year too Anjana Singh is all geared up to rock Doha on Eid. The actress will be seen performing in Doha on December 24. The programme has been organised by Vision group.
Manoj Tiwari, Manoj Tiger, Pradeep Pandey Chintu, Rajkumar R Pandey will also perform at the same event. Anjana Singh also has a number of films lined up for release this year.
